## Anti-Patterns (Avoid)
❌ Anemic domain — business logic outside `domain/`
❌ Kitchen-sink `shared/` — dependency dumping ground
❌ Framework leak into `domain/` — ORM entity in domain layer
❌ Skipping G1 Scope / G2 Design gates (per `.claude/CONTEXT.md`)

